Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Late in the day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,on which the Celestial Dragon's \Nship arrived at the Goa Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,at a small village somewhere \Nin the East Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see the person with \Nthe gigantic face today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've never seen someone like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, the ship is huge, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,580... 581...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,582... 583...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,584...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:55.81,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,You're late, Dragon! I got tired of waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:01.79,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.79,0:05:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,--Oh, that's very bad!\N--Hey, treat him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:14.00,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,Honestly! Where have you been?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I was watching the ceremony \Nfor the Celestial Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:22.61,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,How could you do that without telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.81,0:05:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You attract too much attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:30.21,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,M-My face, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to prepare as soon as \Npossible for what will come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have enough food?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They gave us some at the \Ntraining hall in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's leave here! Head back to Baltigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, in the Goa Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:06:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,after the observers from the \NWorld Government left...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Here comes some junk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,People are doing exactly the \Nsame thing they did before
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,accumulating another mountain of junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?! You're no match for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how strong you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it's nothing if you can't hit a target!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Rubber is not useful in \Nfighting just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! I'm telling you the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All you can do is bounce back \Nattacks and sink like a rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop making fun of the Gum-Gum \NFruit! I'll make you cry someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been creating new attacks \Nstronger than the pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, that was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your arm stretched farther than yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo! You're too easy on Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.49,0:07:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stronger than yesterday as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,--Don't you think so, Sabo?!\N--Don't you think so, Sabo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo was a good brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You mean it'd be \Nbetter if I had died?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You meant it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:07:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:08:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo didn't hit me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,--What?!\N--What?! Be nice to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
