Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.89,0:08:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I hereby establish an independent country.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Country?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:35.93,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"Me too!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
