Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to be strong enough \Nto live on our own!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys belong to Dadan's Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me use your bath sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace! You gotta help me! It's a bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that you wanted \Nto live on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, anybody there in Dadan's Kingdom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.34,0:09:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy got hurt! Please help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:10:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Magra! Please! Treat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, come in now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, it was no joking matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He might have died if the \Ncut was a little bit deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You three fought those beasts \Ntogether, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.68,0:10:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it doesn't prove that you're \Nstrong by fighting on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not good enough at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.97,0:10:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Makino came all the way bringing us sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How to pay respect to other people?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I'm Luffy's brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,it's my job to go see the captain \Nof the Red-Haired Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.73,0:11:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,who helped Luffy in order to thank him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have something to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Alright, I'll teach you how.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, this would be the first one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.09,0:11:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we forgot to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:11:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,--Thank you for the meal!\N--Thank you for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you brats! You got to pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna win today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,--We did it!\N--We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Bear meat stew tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:56.99,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"Seven tears later"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:02.76,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"Ace, 17 years old"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:09.03,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"Luffy, 14 years old"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. See you, Luffy! I'm going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh! I'll be a lot stronger \Nwhen I leave here in 3 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.85,0:14:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You just wait! I'll make my name soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace, son of the Pirate King, has grown up secretly
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.22,0:15:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and he quietly departed from the shore nearby Mt. Corvo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly! I wonder what Garp would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You must raise him, Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Whose baby is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:15:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.01,0:16:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh good. But I can see that \NGarp will be mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He was such an useless little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ace left a message for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! He still has something to \Nsay to me even at the last minute?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He said "Thank you for taking care of me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.74,0:16:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't do that! That fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Boss, are you crying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.31,0:16:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not crying, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to wait 3 years more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! I missed it by a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You almost got it, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you keep the \Ncenter of gravity lower?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.45,0:17:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.47,0:17:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.94,0:17:39.18,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"A few months later"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the newspaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Look here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Ace made his name!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He got his own ship and crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:18:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's great! Ace is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm gonna top him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.37,0:18:12.38,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"Three years later\NLuffy, 17 years old"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.38,0:18:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving now. You're not gonna see me off?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The mayor and Makino won't mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but the people in the Windmill \NVillage will be scared of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just go already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Then you guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say it - I feel awkward!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.34,0:18:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dadan, I don't like mountain bandits...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I like you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop talking nonsense and go \Naway already, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Why am I surrounded by such fools?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.47,0:19:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Windmill Village at the edge of \NGoa Kingdom on the Dawn Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't you take my \Nold fishing boat, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing is gonna sink any minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a small boat...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.09,0:19:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fine! This is \Nwhat I wanna start with!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.50,0:19:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch over me! I'm gonna go out to sea now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.94,0:19:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo was first and Ace was second.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm third but I'm gonna \Ntop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:19:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll catch up with you soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.12,0:20:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing screaming and mumbling?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it some kind of incantation?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not! It's a challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,--Who's Ace?\N--No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'm going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's finally leaving, \Nmayor. I'm gonna miss him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dishonor to the \Nvillage to become a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What nice day for setting sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Here comes our local sea monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know who you're messing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this technique I've \Nbeen training for 10 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.45,0:21:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.76,0:21:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That will learn ya, stupid fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! He beat the sea monster \Nwith a single blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.59,0:21:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's become quite strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.03,0:21:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start with finding a crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.93,0:22:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I want at least 10 of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And the black flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.61,0:22:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.32,0:22:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.03,0:22:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And now,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.60,0:22:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy mourns the loss of his brother Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.68,0:22:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.66,0:22:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pirate King?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.66,0:22:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.70,0:23:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.93,0:23:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.44,0:23:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm too...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.98,0:23:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...weak!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.39,0:23:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As Garp returns to Windmill Village, \NDadan greets him in outrage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Luffy is lost in his grief \Nand helplessness after losing Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.39,0:23:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As he watches Luffy writhe in despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.36,0:23:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe recalls the words of Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.40,0:23:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.87,0:23:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"I Wanna See Them!\NLuffy's Tearful Cry"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.94,0:23:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
